quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  23,43,"Hakuna rudzi (vanhu) rungaita kuti nguva yavo ikasire, kana kuve inonoka"
  23,44,"Uye takave tinotumira vatumwa vedu vachiteverana (umwe mushure memumwe). Nguva dzose paiuya mutumwa wavo kune boka revanhu, vaimuramba; nokudaro takave tinoita kuti vave vanoteverana mukuparadzwa, uye takave tinoita kuti vave nyaya (pakati pevanhu sechidzidzo). Saka ngavave kure avo vanhu vsingatendi"
  23,45,Uye takave tinotuma Musa nemukoma wake Haaroon (Aroni) nezviratidzo zvedu uye nemasimba ari pachena
  23,46,"Kuna Farawo nemakurukota ake, asi vakave vanozvitutumadza, uye vakave vanhu vanozvikudza"
  23,47,"Uye vakataura kuti (Farawo nemakurukota ake): “Tingatenda here mune varume vaviri vakaita sesu, avo vekuti rudzi rwavo varanda vedu?”"
  23,48,"Vakave vanovaramba vose (vari vaviri), uye vakave veavo vakaparadzwa"
  23,49,"Zvirokwazvo, takave tinopa Musa, Gwaro, kuti zvimwe vangave vanotungamirwa"
  23,50,"Uye takave tinoita mwanakomana waMariya uye naamai vake chiratidzo, uye takavachengetedza panzvimbo yakakwirira, nzvimbo yekuzorora, ine chengetedzo uye mvura inoerera"
  23,51,"(Allah vakataura kuti): “Imi vatumwa! Idyai zvakachena, mova munoita mabasa akanaka. Zvirokwazvo, ndinoziva zvikuru zvose zvamunoita.”"
  23,52,"“Uye zvirokwazvo, ichi chitendero chenyu (Islaam) chimwe chete, uye ndini Tenzi venyu. Nokudaro, ivai munonditya.”"
  23,53,"Asi (vanhu) vakave vanopatsanura chitendero chavo pakati pavo mumapoka-poka, boka rimwe nerimwe (boka rose) richifara nezvarinazvo"
  23,54,Saka vasiyei mukurasika kwavo kwekanguva
  23,55,Vanofunga here kuti kuvawedzera muhupfumi nevana
  23,56,Kuti tirikuvapa zvakanaka nekukurumidza? Kwete! (Asi muedzo pasi pano kuti vasave nemugove muhupenyu hwemangwana) asi havazvifungi
  23,57,"Zvirokwazvo, avo vanotya Tenzi vavo vakangwarira"
  23,58,Uye avo vanotenda muzviratidzo zvaTenzi vavo
  23,59,Uye avo vasingasanganisi Tenzi vavo nechimwe chinhu (mukunamata)